quran[142]{c,v,t}:
  6,111,"Sinno Men Jippinno e maЙ“Й“e Malaa'ika, maayЙ“e Й“en yeewtidi e maЙ“Й“e, Men MooЙ“i e maЙ“Й“e kala huunde yeeso maЙ“Й“e ; Й“e laatotanooko gomЙ—imЙ“e si wanaa nde Alla Muuyi. Kono ko Й—uuЙ—i e maЙ“Й“e hino majjaa"
  6,112,"Ko woni nii Men WaЙ—irani kala Annabaajo gaГұo : seytaaneeji yimЙ“e e jinna ; yoga maЙ“Й“e no wahyina e yoga, cuЙ—aari konngol hodo. Sinno Joomi maa Muuyuno, Й“e waЙ—ataani Й—um, tertodu Й“e e ko Й“e fefindotoo"
  6,113,"E fii yo heЙ—ito Й—um, Й“erЙ—e Й“en Й“e gomЙ—inaa laakara, e fii yo Й“e wele Й—um, e fii yo Й“e fefindo huunde nde Й“e fefindotoo"
  6,114,"E ko ko woori Alla mi Й—aЙ“Й“ata Гұaawoowo, ko Kanko woni JippinЙ—o e mo'on ndee Deftere fensitaande? ЖҒen Й“e Men Okki Defte Й“en, hiЙ“e anndi wonnde ko nde Jippinaande immorde ka Joomi maaЙ—a goonga. Wata a jeye e sikkitiiЙ“e Й“en"
  6,115,"Konngol Joomi maaЙ—a ngol timmirii goonga e nunЙ—al. Alaa wattitoowo konnguЙ—i Makko Й—in. Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, AnnduЙ—o"
  6,116,"Si a Й—oftike ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e wonЙ“e ka leydi Й“en, Й“e majjinte e laawol Alla ngol : Й“e wonaalli hiЙ“e jokka si wanaa sikke, Й“e wonaali si wanaa hottotooЙ“e"
  6,117,"Pellet, ko Joomi maa Й“uri Anndude on majjuЙ—o laawol Makko ngol, ko Kanko kadi Й“uri Anndude feewuЙ“e Й“en"
  6,118,Г‘aamee kon ko Innde Alla jantaa e mun si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e Aayeeje Makko Й—en
  6,119,"E ko haЙ—ata on nde on Гұaamataa kon ko Innde Alla jantaa e mun? GomЙ—ii O Fensitanii on kon ko O Harmini e mon, si wanaa kon ko Й“ittorЙ—on e mun. Pellet, ko Й—uuЙ—i [e sirkooЙ“e Й“en] hino majjira mbeleeЙ—e mu'un ko alaa e ganndal. Pellet, ko Joomi Й“uri Anndude jaggitooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,120,"Tertee ko feeГұi e bakkaatu e ko wirnii e mun. Pellet, Й“en faggitotooЙ“e bakkaatu, Й“e yoЙ“oyte kon ko laatinoo hiЙ“e fefindoo"
  6,121,"Wata on Гұaamu kon ko Innde Alla jantaaka e mun, pellet, (salagol) Й—um ko faasiqiyaagal. E pellet, seytaaneeji Й—in no sowonsina e weldiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en no Й“e wennjira on. Si on Й—oftike Й“e, haray pellet, ko on sirkuЙ“e"
  6,122,"E ko on laatinooЙ—o maayЙ—o, Wuurniti mo, Men wuurniti mbo WaЙ—ani mo annoora himo yaara on hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en, wa'ata wa on wonЙ—on e niЙ“e mo wanaa yaltoowo ton? Ko wano non heeferЙ“e Й“en cuЙ—iranaa kon ko Й“e gollaynoo"
  6,123,"Ko wano non Men WaЙ—iri e kala hoЙ—o, mawЙ“e bonЙ“e, fii no Й“e fewjira e mayre. ЖҒe alaa e fewjude si wanaa e ko'e maЙ“Й“e, kono Й“e so'aa anndude"
  6,124,"Si Aaya arii e maЙ“Й“e Й“e wi'a : \"Men gomЙ—intaa haa men okkee sugu ko NulaaЙ“e Alla Й“en okkaa kon\". Ko Alla Й“uri Anndude ka O WaЙ—ata Nulal Makko ngal. Aray ka koyeera e lepte tiiЙ—uЙ—e heЙ“a Й“en bonЙ“e, sabu kon ko Й“e fewjanynoo"
  6,125,"Kala mo Alla Faandii fewnude, O YaГұГұanay=yaajnat Й“ernde makko nden Lislaamu. Kala kadi mo O Faandii Majjinnde, O WaЙ—ay Й“ernde makko nden faaЙ—unde Й“ittunde ; hara himo wa'i wa ЕӢabboowo yaha ka kammu. Ko wano non Alla WaЙ—irta lepte Й—en e Й“en Й“e gomЙ—intaa"
  6,126,Ko Й—um Й—oo woni laawol Joomi maaЙ—a ngol feewungol. GomЙ—ii Men Fensitii Aayeeje Й—en woannde yimЙ“e waajitotooЙ“e
  6,127,Hino woodanibe galle kisal ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e. Ko Kanko woni GiЙ—o maЙ“Й“e sabu kon ko Й“e gollaynoo
  6,128,"Г‘alnde O MooЙ“itoyta Й“e denndaangal : \"Ko onon yo onon yo dental jinna, gomЙ—ii on Й—uЙ—Й—inorii (majjingol) yimЙ“e Й“en\". YiЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en ka yimЙ“e wi'a : \"Joomi amen, yoga amen dakmitorii yoga, men yottike ngal caatal=lajal amen ngal saatinanЙ—aa men\". O Daala : \"Ko Yiite ngen woni werde mon, ko on luttooЙ“e ton, si wanaa kon ko Alla Muuyi\". Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a ko Г‘eeГұuЙ—o, AnnduЙ—o"
  6,129,Ko wano non Men Wurtirta yoga e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en e hoore yoga ; sabu kon ko Й“e faggitotonoo
  6,130,"Ko onon yo dental jinna e yimЙ“e, e araali e mo'on NulaaЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e mo'on, Й“e no fillanoo on Aayeeje Am Й—en, Й“e rentina on hawrugol ndee Й—oo Г‘alaande mon? ЖҒe wi'a : \"Men seedike e hoore pittaali amen\". Nguurndam aduna Й—am hodi Й“e ; Й“e seeditii e hoore pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in wonnde Й“e laatino heeferЙ“e"
  6,131,"ЖҠum ko tawde Joomi maa wonaali halkoowo ca'e sabu tooГұe, hara yimЙ“e majje ko welsindiiЙ“e"
  6,132,Hino woodani kala en darjaaji kon ko Й“e golli. Joomi maa wonaali WelsindiiЙ—o e kon ko Й“e gollata
  6,133,"Ko Joomi ma woni Galo Jom-Yurmeende. Si O Muuyii O NaЙ“ay on, O Lontina Й“aawo mo'on ko O Muuyi ; wano O FuЙ—Й—ornoo on immorde e Й“iЙ—Й“e yimЙ“e goo"
  6,134,"Pellet, ko fodaЙ—on kon ko aray Й—um. On wonaali ronkinooЙ“e [Men]"
  6,135,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, gollee e nokku mo'on, min ko mi golloowo. On anndoyay ko hommbo (e men) laatantoo Й—um battane galle Й—en\". pellet,O malnatah tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,136,"ЖҒe waЙ—anii Alla geЙ“al e ko O Tagi kon immorde e gese e neemoraaЙ—i, Й“e wi'i : \"ЖҠum Й—oo ko Alla -e aaЖҙagol maЙ“Й“e!- ЖҠum Й—oo ko kafidiiЙ—i amen Й—in\". Ko wanani kon kafidiiЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in hewtataa Alla, kono ko wonani kon Alla hewtay kadidiiЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Ko Й“e Гұaawata kon bonii"
  6,137,"Ko wano non kafidiiЙ—i ko heewi e sirkooЙ“e Й“en cuЙ—irani Й“e warugol Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e, fii yo Й—i halkuЙ“e e fii yo Й“e jiiЙ“itu diina maЙ“Й“e kan. Sinno Alla Muuyuno, Й“e waЙ—ataano Й—um. Tertodu Й“e e ko Й“e fefindotoo"
  6,138,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"ЖҠii Й—oo ko neemoraaЙ—i e gese feraaЙ—i : Гұaamataa Й—i si wanaa on mo men yiЙ—i.\"-Ka aaЖҙagol maЙ“Й“e!- E neemoraaЙ—i harminaaЙ—i Й“abbe mun, e neemoraaЙ—i Й—i Й“e jantotaako Innde Alla e mun, fefindagol e Makko ; O YoЙ“oyay Й“e kon ko Й“e fefindotonoo. Ma Alla yobbe fefindagol mu*en ngol"
  6,139,"ЖҒe wi'i kadi: \"Ko woni kon e deedi Й—ii neemoraaЙ—i, ko heeranii Й—um worЙ“e amen, harmani rewЙ“e amen\". Si Й—um wonii ko jiibuЙ—um, kamЙ“e ko Й“e kafooЙ“e Й—um. O YoЙ“oyay Й“e ko Й“e hanndi kon. Kanko ko O Г‘eeГұuЙ—o, AnnduЙ—o"
  6,140,"GomЙ—ii sooyii Й“en warirЙ“e Й“iЙ—Й“e mun njofoyaagal ko aldaa e ganndal, Й“e harminiri kon ko Alla Arsiki Й“e fefindagol e hoore Alla. GomЙ—ii Й“e majjii, Й“e wonaano feewuЙ“e"
  6,141,"Ko Kanko woni On FuЙ—Й—uЙ—o gese waЙ—aaЙ—e bente e Й—e waЙ—aaka bente, e tamarooje, e remuruuji sertuЙ—i Гұaamndu mu'un, e nebbanteeje, e rummaana nannduЙ—e e Й—e nanndaa. Г‘aamee e dimЙ—e majje si Й—e rimii, jonnon asakal mun Гұalnde soГұaa. Wata on Й“urtin, pellet, Kanko O YiЙ—aa Й“urtinooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,142,"Hino e neemoraaЙ—i Й—in ronndotooЙ—i e joltuЙ—i. Г‘aamee e kon ko Alla Arsiki on, wata on jokku taaЙ“aЕӢlle seytaane Й—en, pellet, kanko ko o gaГұo mon feeГұuЙ—o"
  6,143,"[O Taganii on] nooneeji jeetati : no e baali Й—in Й—iЙ—i, no e be'i Й—in kadi Й—iЙ—i. Maaku : \"E ko gori Й—in Й—iЙ—i O Harmini kaa ko deyi Й—in Й—iЙ—i, kaa ko ko woni e nder renngaaji deyi Й—in Й—iЙ—i? Humpitiree lam ganndal si on laatike goonguЙ“e"
  6,144,"No e gelooЙ—i Й—in Й—iЙ—i, no e na'i Й—in kadi Й—iЙ—i. Maaku : \"E ko gori Й—in Й—iЙ—i O Harmini kaa ko deyi Й—in Й—iЙ—i, kaa ko ko woni e nder renngaaji deyi Й—in Й—iЙ—i, kaa on seedino tuma Alla Wasiyinoo on Й—um?\" Kohommbo Й“uri tooГұude haa fota wa on fefindiiЙ—o fenaande e hoore Alla fii no o majjiniri yimЙ“e Й“en ko aldaa e ganndal? Pellet, Alla Fewnataa yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,145,"Maaku : \"Mi tawaali e kon ko wahyinaa e am, ko harminaa e Гұaamoowo mo no Гұaama Й—um, si wanaa nde laatotoo ko maayi (jiibi), maa ЖҙiiЖҙam sankotooЙ—am, maa teewu kose -sabu Й—um ko soЙ“e- maa (ko hirsiraa) faasiqiyaagal\". Kala on Й“ittiiЙ—o, hara wanaa bewЙ—o, wanaa jaggituЙ—o, haray pellet, Joomi maa ko Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  6,146,"Ko en Й“en AlyahuudaaЙ“e (tun) woni ko Men Harmini kala ko jogii peЙ—aali. Na'i Й—in e dammi Й—in kadi, Men Harminii e maЙ“Й“e Й“elle majji Й—en, si wanaa ko Й“abbe majji ronndii, maa tete on, maa ko jillondiri e Жҙi'e. Ko Й—um Men YoЙ“irnoo Й“e berwre maЙ“Й“e nden. Pellet, ko Men GoonguЙ“e"
  6,147,"Si Й“e fennii ma, maaku : \"Joomi mon ko Jom-Yurmeende yaajunde, lepte Makko Й—en ruttetaake e yimЙ“e bomЙ“e Й“en"
  6,148,"Arma sirkuЙ“e Й“en wi'a : \"Sinno Alla Muuyuno, men sirkataano, wanaa baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en, men harmintaano kadi hay e huunde\". Ko non Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e fennirnoo haa Й“e meeЙ—i lepte Amen Й—en. Maaku : \"Hara ganndal no woodani on yaltinanon men ngal? Pellet, on jokkaa si wanaa sikke, onon on wonaali si wanaa fenooЙ“e"
  6,149,"Maaku : \"Ko Alla woodani hujja yottiiЙ—o on.Sinno O Muuyuno, O Fewnayno on denndaangal"
  6,150,"Maaku : \"Addee seedeeЙ“e mon Й“en, Й“e seeditoo wonnde Alla Harminii Й—um Й—oo\". Si Й“e seedike, wata a seedodu e maЙ“Й“e. Wata a jokku mbeleeЙ—e Й“en fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en e Й“en Й“e gomЙ—inaa laakara, kamЙ“e hiЙ“e sirkana Joomi maЙ“Й“e"
  6,151,"Maaku : \"Aree mi janngana on ko Joomi mo Harmini e mon : ko nde kafidoton e Makko huunde, waЙ—anon jibimЙ“e mon Й“en moЖҙЖҙere. Wata on waru Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en kulol immorde e baasal. Ko Menen Arsikata on e kamЙ“e. Wata on Й“aЙ—to pankare Й—en ko feeГұi e majje e ko wirnii. Wata waru wonkii ki Alla Harmini si wanaa e goonga. Ko Й—um mooЙ—on O Wasiyii on ; belajo'o, on haqqilay"
  6,152,"Wata on Й“aЙ—to jawdi wonduЙ—o si wanaa hara ko no Й“uri moЖҙЖҙirde, haa o yottoo kellefuyee makko. Timminiree etirЙ—e Й—en e manndikirЙ—e= peesirde Й—en no nunЙ—iri. Men fawaa wonkii si wanaa ko ki townata. Si on wowlay nunЙ—ee hay si ko e hoore jom-Й“aЙ—todal. Ahadi Alla ndin hunnon. Ko Й—um mooЙ—on woni ko O Wasiyii on; belajo'o, on annditay"
  6,153,"E wonnde pellet, Й—um Й—oo ko laawol am focciingol, jokkee ngol ; wata on jokku laawoy senndaykoy on e laawol Makko ngol\". Ko Й—um mooЙ—on woni ko O Wasiyii on ; belajo'o, on rentoto"
  6,154,"Refti Men Okki Muusaa Deftere nden timmirnde (neema) mo o moЖҙЖҙiniri, fensitunde kala huunde, ko nde peewal e yurmeende ; belajo'o, Й“e gomЙ—inay hawrygol e Jommi maЙ“Й“e"
  6,155,"Ndee Й—oo ko Deftere (Alqur'aana), Men Jippiinde ko nde barkinnde - jokkee nde, rentoЙ—on ; belajo'o, on yurmedon"
  6,156,"Fii wata on wi'oy : \"Defte Й—en ko e feddeeji Й—iЙ—i Jippinaa, ado amen, men laatinoke welsindiiЙ“e janngugol Й—e"
  6,157,"maa Й—um wi'on : \"Sinno menen, Deftere nden Jippinano e amen, men laatotono Й“urЙ“e Й“en Й—on feewude\". GomЙ—ii arii on immorde ka Joomi mon, Й“anngannduyee, e peewal, e yurmeende. Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГұude haa hewta on fennuЙ—o Aayeeje Alla Й—en o Й—uurnii Й—e. Arma Men YoЙ“iroya Й“en Й—uurnotooЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en lepte bonЙ—e, sabu ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e Й—uurnoo"
  6,158,"Hara Й“ee no habbii si wanaa nde Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en ara e maЙ“Й“e? Maa Joomi maa Ara? Maa yoga e Maandeeji Joomi maa ara? Г‘alnde yoga e Maandeeji Joomi maa ari, nafataa wonkii gomЙ—inal makki, ki laatanooki gomЙ—inki ko adii, maa ki faggitii e gomЙ—inal makki moЖҙЖҙere. Maaku : \"Habbitee! Menen ko men habbitiiЙ“e"
  6,159,"Pellet, Й“en sennduЙ“e diina mun kan, Й“e laatii feddeeji, a jeyaaka e maЙ“Й“e e huunde : Anndee fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e ko faade ka Alla. Refti O Humpita Й“e ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e golla"
  6,160,Kala arduЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙere hino woodani mo sappo yeru mayre ; kala kadi arduЙ—o e bone o yoЙ“itetaake si wanaa yeru makko. KamЙ“e Й“e tooГұetaake
  6,161,"Maaku : \"Min, Joomi am Fewni lam faade e laawol focciingol, diina ГұiiЙ“uka, diina Ibraahiima, ooГұiiЙ—o [e diina meere] ; o jeyanooka e sirkooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,162,"Maaku : \"Pellet, julde am nden, e kirse am Й—en, e nguurndam am Й—am, e maayde am nden, ko All woodani, JeyЙ—o Winndere nden"
  6,163,"KafidiiЙ—o alanaa Mo! Ko Й—um mi yamiraa, ko mi woni arano e jebbiliiЙ“e Й“en"
  6,164,"Maaku : \"E ko tanaa Alla mi Й—aЙ“Й“ata reweteeЙ—o, ko Kanko woni JeyЙ—o kala huunde?! Kala wonkii faggitantaako si wanaa e hoore-makki : wonkii ronndotaako bone wonkii goo. Refti ko faade ka Joomi mon woni ruttorde mon, O Humpita on kon ko luutondiraynoЙ—on e mun"
  6,165,"Ko Kanko woni WaЙ—uЙ—o on lontiiЙ“e ka keydi, O ЖҒamtiri yoga mon dow yoga, darjaaji ; fii yo O Jarribo on e ko O Okki on. Pellet, Joomi maa ko yaawuЙ—o lepte, Kanko kadi, ko O Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  7,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim, Saad"
  7,2,"Ko Deftere Jippinaande e maaЙ—a, wata Й“itteende wonu ka Й“ernde maa e mayre ; fii yo a waajor nde, ko nde waaju wonannde gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  7,3,"Jokkee ko Jippinaa e mon kon immorde ka Joomi mon, wata on jokku gaanin Й—um, weldiiЙ“e, fanЙ—ii ko waajitotoЙ—on"
  7,4,"ЖҠuuЙ—ii e ca'e Й—e Men halki! Lepte Amen Й—en ari e majje jemma hiЙ“e waalii Й—aanii, maa hara ko Й“e fowtiiЙ“e Гұalorma"
  7,5,"Noddaandu maЙ“Й“e ndun Й“aawo lepte Amen Й—en arde Й“e, wonaano si naa wi'ugol : \"Menen men laatino tooГұooЙ“e"
  7,6,"Ma Men Lamnditoyo Й“en Й“e (Men) Nulunoo e mun, Ma Men Lamnditoyo kadi NulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  7,7,Ma Men Fillanoroyo Й“e (golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en) e ganndal. Men wonaano wirniiЙ“e
  7,8,"Manndakke=peesgol Й—en nde Г‘alnde, ko Й—e goonga. Kala mo manndake (moЖҙЖҙi Й—en) teddi, ko Й“en Й—on woni maloyteeЙ“e Й“en"
  7,9,"Kala mo manndakke (moЖҙЖҙi) mun foygitii=hoyi, ko Й“en Й—on woni sooyinirЙ“e pittaali mu'un saЙ“u ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e yedda Aayeeje Amen Й—en"
  7,10,"GomЙ—ii Men Newinanii on ke leydi, Men WaЙ—ani on e mayri nguuree. (Kono) fanЙ—ii ko yettoton"
  7,11,"GomЙ—ii Men tagii on, refti Men Mbaadini on, refti Men Wi'ani Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en : \"Sujjanee Aadama\", Й“e sujji, si wanaa Ibliisa, o jeyanooka e sujjuЙ“e Й“en"
  7,12,"O Daali : \"Ko haЙ—u-maa nde sujjataa nde Mi Yamir-maa?\" O wi'i : \"MiЙ—o Й“uri mo moЖҙЖҙude : A Tagii lam immorde e Yiite, A Tagii mo immorde e loopal"
  7,13,"O Daali : \"Jippo ton, haananaama nde mawnintintoЙ—aa ton. Yaltu, an ko a jeyaaЙ—o e hoyЙ“e Й“en"
  7,14,"[Ibliisa] wi'i : \"Nennitanam haa Гұalnde Й“e immintintee"
  7,15,"[Alla] Daali : \"An, ko a jeyaaЙ—o e nennitanteeЙ“e Й“en"
  7,16,"[Ibliisa] wi'i : \"Sabu ko bewinirЙ—aa lam kon, ma mi jooЙ—ano Й“e ka laawol Maa focciingol"
  7,17,"Refti mi ardiranay Й“e yeeso maЙ“Й“e e Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e, e ka e Гұaame maЙ“Й“e e ka nane maЙ“Й“e. A tawataa ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e ko yettooЙ“e [Ma]"
  7,18,"[Alla] Daali : \"Yaltu ton, ko a ЕӢiГұaaЙ—o raЙ—aaЙ—o. Kala jokkuЙ—o ma e maЙ“Й“e, ma Mi hebbiiroy Jahannama onon denndaangal"
  7,19,"Ko an yo Aadama, hoЙ—u an e Й“eyngu maa ka Aljanna, Гұaamee kala nokku ka yiЙ—u-Й—on ; wata tun on Й“aЙ—to ngal Й—oo leggal, sakko laatoЙ—on e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,20,"Seytaane sowinsini Й“e, fii yo o feГұГұinan Й“e ko suuЙ—aa e maЙ“Й“e e awraaji maЙ“Й“e, o wi'i : \"Joomi mon haЙ—iraali on ngal leggal si wanaa fii wata on laato Malaa'ika maa laatoЙ—on duumotooЙ“e [ka Aljanna]"
  7,21,"O woondani Й“e o wi'i : \"Min ko mi laaЙ“anooЙ“e on"
  7,22,"O hodiri Й“e janfa. Nde Й“e meeЙ—unoo laggal ngal, awraaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in feeГұani Й“e, Й“e waЙ—ti hiЙ“e surritora kaaki Aljanna Й—in. Joomi maЙ“Й“e noddi Й“e : \"E Mi haЙ—aano on e ngal leggal, Mi wi'ani on : Pellet, seytaane ko gaГұo mo'on Й“annguЙ—o"
  7,23,"ЖҒe wi'idi Й“e Й—iЙ—o : \"Joomi amen, men tooГұii ko'e amen. Si A haforanaali men yurmeЙ—aa men, ma men jeye e sooyuЙ“e Й“en"
  7,24,"[Alla] Daali : \"Jippee (ka leydi), yoga mon ko ayЙ“e yoga. Hino woodani on ka leydi ton ГұiiЙ“irde e dakamme haa saanga"
  7,25,"[Alla] Daali : \"Ko (ka leydi) ton wuuroton, ko ton kadi maayoton, ko e mayri kadi yaltinoyteЙ—on"
  7,26,"Ko onon yo Й“iЙ—Й“e Aadam! GomЙ—ii Men Jippinii e mo'on conci surrayЙ—i awraaji mon Й—in e cuЙ—aari. -Ko cocni kulol Й—in non Й“uri muЖҙЖҙude.- Ko Й—um jeyaaЙ—um e Aayeeje Alla. Belajo'o, kamЙ“e Й“e waajitoto"
  7,27,"Ko onon yo Й“iЙ—Й“e Aadama! Wata seytaane fitinir on wano o yaltinirnoo baabiraaЙ“e mon Й“en ka Aljanna, himo Й“oora e maЙ“Й“e conci maЙ“Й“e Й—in fii yo hollu Й“e awraaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Pellet, himo reeni on kanko e gorol makko ngol nokku ka on yi'ataa Й“e. Menen Men waЙ—ii seytaaneeji Й—in weldiiЙ—i Й“en Й“en gomЙ—intaa"
  7,28,"Si Й“e waЙ—ii pankare, Й“e wi'a : \"Men tawru Й—um baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en, ko Alla yamiri men Й—um\". Maaku : \"Pellet, Alla yamirtaa pankare. E on wowlay e hoore Alla ko on anndaa"
  7,29,"Maaku : \"Joomi am yamirii nunЙ—al. Г‘iiЙ“non geece mon Й—en nokku kala e ka juuloton, tororon Mo laЙ“Й“inangol Mo diina kan. Ko wano O FuЙ—Й—ori on non ruttirton"
  7,30,"Fedde goo O fewnii, fedde goo majjere nden jojji e hoore maЙ“Й“e. KamЙ“e Й“e jogitike seytaaneeji Й—in weldiiЙ“e gaanin Alla, kamЙ“e hiЙ“e sikka ko Й“e feewuЙ“e"
  7,31,"Ko onon yo Й“iЙ—Й“e Aadama, Жҙettee cuЙ—aari mon ndin nokku kala ka juuloton. Г‘aamee yaron wata on fantin. Pellet, Kanko O yiЙ—aa fantinooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,32,"Maaku : \"Ko hommbo harmini cuЙ—aari Alla ndi O Yaltinani jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, e laaЙ“uЙ—i Й—in ka arsikeeji?\" Maaku : \"ЖҠin Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e ka nguurndam aduna woodani, heeraniiЙ—i [Й“e] Г‘alnde Darngal\". Ko wano non Men Fensitirta Aayeeje Й—en, woanannde yimЙ“e anndooЙ“e"
  7,33,"Maaku : \"Joomi am ko Harmini : ko pankare Й—en -ko feeГұi e majje ko suuЙ—ii-, e bakkaatu, e bewrugol ko aldaa e goonga, e nde sirkanton Mo kon ko O Jippinanaali Й—um hujja, e nde wowloton e Alla ko on anndaa"
  7,34,"Hino woodani kala mofte laja. Si lajal maЙ“Й“e ngal arii, Й“e nennitantaake saa'i gooto, Й“e ardinantaake kadi"
  7,35,"Ko onon yo Й“iЙ—Й“e Aadama! Si aroyii e mon NulaaЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e mo'on, Й“e no fillanoo on Aayeeje Am, kala hulЙ—o [Alla] o moЖҙЖҙini [golle], kulol alanaa Й“en Й—on, wanaa kamЙ“e kadi sunoytoo"
  7,36,"ЖҒen fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en Й“e townitanii e heЙ—e, ko Й“en woni yimЙ“e Yiite, kamЙ“e ko Й“e luttooЙ“e ton"
  7,37,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГұuЙ—o haa hewta on fefindiiЙ—o e Alla fenaande, maa o fenni Aayeeje Makko Й—en? ЖҒen heЙ“ay Й“e geЙ“al maЙ“Й“e ngal e binndoodi ndin ; haa si NulaaЙ“e Amen [warooЙ“e] Й“en arii Й“e, Й“e wara Й“e, Й“e wi'a : \"Ko honto kon ko rewaynoЙ—on gaanin Alla [woni]?!\" ЖҒe wi'a : \"ЖҠi majjirii men\". ЖҒe seeditoo e ko'e maЙ“Й“e, wonnde Й“e laatino yedduЙ“e"
  7,38,"[Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en] wi'a : \"Naate e moftaaji, gomЙ—ii yawtii ado mon immorde e jinna e yimЙ“e ka nder Yiite\". Tuma kala nde mofte naati, Й—e huЙ—a banndam majje. Haa si Й“e tawtindirii ton Й“e denndaanal, sakkitiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en wi'ana aramЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en : \"Joomi amen! Ko Й“ee majjini men : Okku Й“e lepte cowanЙ—e e Yiite ngen\". O Daala : \"Hino woodani kala [mon] cowanЙ—e, kono on anndaa"
  7,39,"AramЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en wi'ana sakkitiiЙ“e Й“en : \"Alanaa on e dow amen Й“ural, meeЙ—iree lepte Й—en sabu kon ko faggitotonoЙ—on"
  7,40,"Pellet, Й“en fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“e townitanii Й—e, Й“e udditantaake dame kammuuli Й—in, Й“e naatataa kadi Aljanna haa ngelooba naata e wuddere meselal. Ko wano non Men yoЙ“irte Й“omЙ“e Й“en"
  7,41,"Hino woodani Й“e ka Jahannama ndaЙ—Й—udi, no dow maЙ“Й“e kadi kippoodi. Ko wanon non Men yoЙ“irta tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,42,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i - Men fawataa wonkii si wanaa ko ki waawi - Ko Й“en Й—on woni yimЙ“e Aljanna : kamЙ“e ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ton"
  7,43,"Men Й“oori e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en konnaagu, canЙ—i Й—in no ila senngo ley maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wi'a : \"Yettoore woodani Alla On fewuЙ—o men e Й—um Й—oo, men wonaano feewooЙ“e si Alla fewnaano men. GomЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e Joomi amen Й“en addii goonga\". ЖҒe noddee si ko woni : \"On Й—on mooЙ—on Aljanna, on roninaama mo, sabu kon ko gollaynoЙ—on"
  7,44,"YimЙ“e Aljanna Й“en noddi yimЙ“e Yiite Й“en, si ko woni : \"GomЙ—ii men tawii ko Joomi amen fodi men kon ko goonga. Onon kadi on tawii ko Joomi mon fodi on kon ko goonga?\" ЖҒe wi'i : \"Eyyo\". Noddoowo nodda hakkunde maЙ“Й“e wonnde : Kuddi Alla ndin wonii e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,45,"ЖҒen sakkotooЙ“e=falatoobe gaay e laawol Alla ngol, Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ana ngol ooГұorde, kamЙ“e kadi ko Й“e yedduЙ“e laakara"
  7,46,"Heedo no hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Hino e dow tulde La'raafi nden worЙ“e hiЙ“e anndira kala e maande mun. ЖҒe nodda yimЙ“e Aljanna Й“en, si ko woni : \"Kisiyee woni e mon!\". ЖҒe naataali mo kono hiЙ“e tamЖҙinii"
  7,47,"Si giiЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en fewtiniraa Й“annge yimЙ“e Yiite Й“en, Й“e wi'a : \"Joomi amen! Wata A waЙ—tidu men e yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,48,"YimЙ“e La'raafi Й“en noddi worЙ“e, hiЙ“e anndira Й“en maandeeji maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wi'a : \"Nafaali on mooЙ“ugol mon [jawle], e kon ko laatinoЙ—on hiЙ—on mawnintinoo"
  7,49,"E ko Й“ee Й—oo woondirnoЙ—on [wonnde] Alla memintaa Й“e yurmeende?! Naatee Aljanna! Kulol alanaa on, wanaa onon woni ko sunoytoo"
  7,50,"YimЙ“e Yiite Й“en noddi yimЙ“e Aljanna Й“en, si ko woni : \"Yuppee e amen ndiyam, maa kon ko Alla arsiki on\". ЖҒe wi'a: \"Pellet, Alla harmini Й—in Й—iЙ—i e heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  7,51,"ЖҒen jogitoriiЙ“e diina mun kan mbeleeЙ—e e fijindaaru, nguurndam aduna hodi Й“e. Hannde Men yejjitiray Й“e no Й“e yejjitirnoo hawrugol Г‘alaande maЙ“Й“e ndee, e kon ko Й“e yeddiraynoo Aayeeje Amen Й—en"
  7,52,"GomЙ—ii Men addanii Й“e Deftere, Men fensitiri nde e dow anndal, ko nde peewal e yurmeende Й“en yimЙ“e gomЙ—inooЙ“e"
  7,53,"Hara hiЙ“e habbii si wanaa battane mun Й—en? Г‘alnde battane (firo) mayre arata, yejjitunooЙ“e Й—um Й“en ko adii wi'ay : \"GomЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e Joomi amen Й“en addii goonga. Hara tefooЙ“e no woodani men Й“e tefana men? Maa men ruttee [aduna] men golla ko wanaa ko men gollaaynoo?\" GomЙ—ii Й“e hayrinii wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e ; kon ko Й“e fefindotonoo majjiriЙ“e"
  7,54,"Pellet, Joomi mon ko Alla, On TaguЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e nder balЙ—e jeegoo, refti O fotondiri ka hoore Arsi. Himo suddira jemma on Гұalorma, hiЙ—i Й—aЙ“Й“indira no yaccorii. Naange ngen e lewru ndun e koode Й—en ko eltiraaЙ—i yamiroore Makko. Faamee ko Kanko heeranii tagu ngun e yamiroore nden. Mawnii mawngu Alla, JeyЙ—o Winndere nden. @Corrected"
  7,55,"Noddiiree Joomi mon yankinaare e gunndoo. Pellet, Kanko O YiЙ—aa jaggitooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,56,"Wata on bonnu ke leydi Й“aawo moЖҙЖҙugol ndi. Noddiree Mo kulol e tama'u. Pellet, yumeende Alla nden no Й“adii moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e Й“en"
  7,57,"Ko Kanko woni Nuloowo keneeli Й—in welo-welo yeeso Yurmeende Makko nden. Haa si ndu ronndike duulere teddunde, Men Sogga nde e leydi maayndi [yoori], Men Jippina e mayri ndiyam, Men Yaltinira Й—am kala dimЙ—e. Ko non Men Yaltiniroyta maayЙ“e Й“en. Belajo'o, on waajitoto"
  7,58,"Leydi moЖҙЖҙiri ndin, puЙ—i mayri no yaltira duЕӢayee Joomi mayri ; ndin ndi (puЙ—i mun) boni, ndi yaltintaa si wanaa no saЙ—tiri. Ko non Men ЖҒannginirta Aayeeje Й—en woannde yimЙ“e yettooЙ“e [Joomi mun]"
  7,59,"GomЙ—ii Men Nulii Nuuhu e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, o maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, rewee Alla. ReweteeЙ—o alanaa on ko woori Mo. Min miЙ—o hulani on lepte Г‘alaande mawnde"
  7,60,"HooreeЙ“e mbatu yimЙ“e makko Й“en wi'i : \"Menen meЙ—en yi'e e nder majjere Й“anngunde"
  7,61,"O maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, majjere (woo) alaa e am ; ko woni min, ko NulaaЙ—o immorde ka JeyЙ—o Winndere nden"
  7,62,"MiЙ—o yottina e mon Nule Joomi am, miЙ—o laaЙ“ana on (reedu), miЙ—o anndi ka Alla ko on anndaa"
  7,63,"E on haawi fii waaju no ari on immorde ka Joomi mon e dow gorko jeyaaЙ—o e mo'on?! Fii yo o jertin on e fii yo on rento, belajo'o, on (heЙ“ay) yurmeende [Alla]"
  7,64,"ЖҒe fenni mo. Men daЙ—ndii mo e Й“en wonnduЙ“e e makko ka laana, Men yooli Й“en fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en. Pellet, Й“e laatino yimЙ“e wumiЙ—uЙ“e"
  7,65,"[Men Nulii] kadi faade e AadinkooЙ“e Й“en, musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on Huudi. O maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, rewee Alla, reweteeЙ—o alanaa on ko woori mo. E on hulataa [Mo]"
  7,66,"HooreeЙ“e mbatu Й“en yedduЙ“e e yimЙ“e makko Й“en wi'i : \"Menen meЙ—en yi'e e Й—ayre, menen meЙ—en sikku maa jeyaaЙ—o e fenooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,67,"O maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, Й—ayre (woo) alaa e am ; ko woni min, ko NulaaЙ—o immorde ka JeyЙ—o Winndere nden"
  7,68,"MiЙ—o yottina e mo'on Nule Joomi am, min (non) ko mi laaЙ“anoo on (reedu), hoolniiЙ—o"
  7,69,"E haawnu on fii waaju no ari on immorde ka Joomi mon e dow gorko jeyaaЙ—o e mo'on, fii yo o jertin on?! Janntee tuma nde O WaЙ—unoo on lontiiЙ“e Й“aawo yimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“en, O Й“eydi on ka tagu cemmbe. Jantee neemaaji Alla Й—in belajo'o, on malete"
  7,70,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"E a aru e amen fii yo men rewu Alla tun, men acca kon ko baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en rewaynoo?! Awa addan men ko foduЙ—aa men kon (e lepte) si tawii ko a jeyaaЙ—o e goognuЙ“e Й“en"
  7,71,"O maaki : \"GomЙ—ii yanii e mon immorde ka Joomi mon soЙ“e (lepte) e tikkere. E on wenjay lam fii inЙ—e Й—e innuЙ—on onon e baabiraaЙ“e mo'on, Alla Jippinaali fii majje hujja?! Faditee! Min, wonndude e mo'on, ko mi jeyaaЙ—o e faditiiЙ“e Й“en"
  7,72,"Men daЙ—ndiri mo e Й“en wonnduЙ“e e makko yurmeende Amen, Men taЖҙi Й“abbe Й“en fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“e laatanooki gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  7,73,"[Men Nulii] kadi faade e Samuuda'en, musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on Saalihu, o maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, rewee Alla. ReweteeЙ—o alanaa on ko woori Mo. GomЙ—ii arii on Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi mon : mbaa ko ngelooba Alla maande wonannde on, tertee mba Гұaama ka leydi Alla, wata on memir mba bone sakko lepte muusuЙ—e nannga on"
  7,74,"Annditee tuma nde O waЙ—unoo on lontiiЙ“e AadinkooЙ“e Й“en, O weerni on ka leydi hiЙ—on jogitoo e ndantaaji mayri kuЙ“eeje, hiЙ—on lesa pelle (waЙ—on) cuuЙ—i. Annditee neemaaji Alla Й—in, wata on Й“urtinir ka leydi ko on bonnooЙ“e"
  7,75,"HooreeЙ“e mbatu mawnintiniiЙ“e Й“en e yimЙ“e makko Й“en wi'ani gomЙ—imЙ“e lo'inaaЙ“e Й“en e maЙ“Й“e : \"E hiЙ—on anndi wonnde Saalihu ko NulaaЙ—o immorde ka Joomi makko?\" ЖҒe wi'i : Menen ko men gomЙ—imЙ“e ko o Nulidaa e mun kon"
  7,76,"ЖҒen mawnintiniiЙ“e wi'i : \"Menen, kon ko gomЙ—inЙ—on, ko men yedduЙ“e Й—um"
  7,77,"ЖҒe borii ngelooba mban, Й“e mawnintinii gaay e yamiroore Joomi maЙ“Й“e nden, Й“e wi'i : \"Ko an yo Saalihu, addan men kon ko foduЙ—aa men (e lepte) si tawii ko a jeyaaЙ—o e NulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  7,78,"Dillaango ngon nanngi Й“e, Й“e waЙ—tini ka koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e jicciiЙ“e-Й—aanii"
  7,79,"O hucci Й“e o maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, gomЙ—ii mi yottinii e mon Nulal Joomi am ngal mi laaЙ“anii on (reedu), konnon, on yiЙ—aa laaЙ“ooЙ“e (reedu) Й“en"
  7,80,"E luuti, tuma nde o maakannoo yimЙ“e makko Й“en : \" E o aray pankare Й—e goЙ—Й—o goo adaaki on e mun e Winndere nden"
  7,81,"Onon hiЙ—on yottoo e worЙ“e Й“en tuuyo accon rewЙ“e Й“en! Si ko woni, onon ko on yimЙ“e fantimЙ“e"
  7,82,"Jaabawol makko Й“en wonaano si wanaa ko Й“e wi'i : \"Yaltinee Й“e ka hoЙ—o mon ; kamЙ“e ko Й“e yimЙ“e laЙ“Й“intintooЙ“e"
  7,83,"Men daЙ—ndi mo kanko e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, si wanaa debbo makko on ; onЙ—on heddoduno e (leptaaЙ“e) Й“en"
  7,84,Men saaЖҙini toЙ“o e maЙ“Й“e. Ndaarii ko honno battane bomЙ“e Й“en laatornoo
  7,85,"[Men Nulii] kadi faade e Madyana, musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on Su'aybu, o maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, rewee Alla. ReweteeЙ—o alanaa on ko woori Mo. GomЙ—ii Й“anngannduyee arii on immorde ka Joomi mon. Timminee etirЙ—e Й—en e manndikke Й—en, wata on Й—uytan yimЙ“e Й“en piiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, wata on bonnu ko leydi Й“aawo moЖҙЖҙugol ndi. Ko Й—um mooЙ—on Й“uri on moЖҙЖҙannde si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  7,86,"Wata on jooЙ—o e kala laawol, hiЙ—on kammba, hiЙ—on sakko=faloo e laawol Alla ngol Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Mo, hiЙ—on Й—aЙ“Й“ana ngol ooГұaare. Annditee tuma nde wonnoЙ—on seeЙ—aaЙ“e O Й—uЙ—Й—ini on. Ndaaree honno battane bonnooЙ“e Й“en laatornoo"
  7,87,"Si wonii fedde e mooЙ—on gomЙ—inii kon ko Nuliraa e mun, fedde goo gomЙ—inaali, muГұГұee haa Alla Гұaawa hakkunde me'en. Ko Kanko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ГұaawooЙ“e Й“en"